<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Dragon Claw</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#0b0b12;
color:white;
}

/* Navbar */

header{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:20px 80px;
}

.logo{
font-size:22px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#8c6cff;
}

nav a{
margin-left:25px;
text-decoration:none;
color:white;
opacity:0.8;
}

nav a:hover{
opacity:1;
}

/* Hero */

.hero{
text-align:center;
padding:140px 20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:64px;
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#8c6cff,#00eaff);
-webkit-background-clip:text;
color:transparent;
}

.hero p{
max-width:600px;
margin:auto;
margin-top:20px;
opacity:0.8;
}

.hero button{
margin-top:30px;
padding:15px 35px;
border:none;
background:#8c6cff;
color:white;
border-radius:8px;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
}

/* Features */

.features{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
gap:30px;
padding:100px 20px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.card{
background:#14141c;
padding:30px;
border-radius:12px;
width:260px;
text-align:center;
}

.card h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#8c6cff;
}

/* How it works */

.steps{
padding:100px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.steps-container{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
gap:40px;
margin-top:40px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.step{
background:#14141c;
padding:30px;
border-radius:10px;
width:250px;
}

/* Footer */

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:40px;
opacity:0.6;
border-top:1px solid #222;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="logo">DragonClaw</div>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Features</a>
<a href="#">Docs</a>
<a href="#">Launch App</a>
<a href="https://x.com/dragonclaw_bot" target="_blank">X</a>
</nav>

</header>


<section class="hero">

<h1>AI Agents For Your Business</h1>

<p>
Automate support, handle leads, and communicate with customers
using intelligent AI agents across voice, text and web.
</p>

<button>Launch App</button>

</section>


<section class="features">

<div class="card">
<h3>AI Voice Agent</h3>
<p>Handle inbound and outbound calls with intelligent voice AI.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Web Chat AI</h3>
<p>Convert website visitors into leads with smart chat agents.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Automation</h3>
<p>Automate emails, SMS and support tasks 24/7.</p>
</div>

</section>


<section class="steps">

<h2>How It Works</h2>

<div class="steps-container">

<div class="step">
<h3>1. Setup</h3>
<p>Define how your AI agent should interact with customers.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>2. Training</h3>
<p>The AI agent learns your business data and workflows.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>3. Launch</h3>
<p>Deploy your AI agent to voice, chat and messaging channels.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>


<footer>

<p>© 2026 Dragon Claw </p>

</footer>


</body>
</html>
